Step 5 — What Dye Tests Reveal

In real systems, dye tests show three things:

True pathways

Where flow actually happens.

Dead zones

Parts of the system that look important but carry no flow.

Feedback loops

Where output returns to influence input.

Those loops are usually the most powerful parts.

